{"word":"συμμεταβάλλω","slug":"συμμεταβάλλω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συμμεταβάλλω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-βᾰλῶ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to change along with</i> other things, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to change sides and take part with</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> in <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a> <i>to change with</i> or <i>together</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}